revision.text: *Note: Minimum attack is calculated without taking into consideration click attack or the Pokémon's type(s). You can see how much damage you do against a certain Pokémon by clicking on or scrolling over the "Pokémon attack" number below the battle screen. The [[Type Effectiveness]] page has more information on how type matchups are ruled in Pokéclicker.
